# Font Licensing

## Google Sans
Google Sans is a proprietary font by Google Inc.
- https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Google+Sans
License: Proprietary — not publicly downloadable.
Place TTF files in this directory manually, or remove "Google Sans"
from FONT_FAMILY in variables.json to use fallback fonts.

## Material Symbols
Material Symbols are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
- https://github.com/google/material-design-icons
- https://fonts.google.com/icons
License: Apache 2.0
Downloaded automatically by scripts/download_fonts.py.
